Find more: http://TheBlaze.com/TV

In this "illuminating moment in American history" (as first seen on TheBlaze TV show "Liberty Treehouse"), find out about the history of Tupperware, created in the 1940s by Earl Silas Tupper. See his miraculous story - from DuPont plastics worker to millionaire inventor of a product used by people all over the world today.
